{"tid":2205510,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[forked] [9up數學]0.9999... = 1 的迷思","createTime":"2020-09-17T01:30:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T11:21:36.000Z","uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8791502cd3375e88cbf66f19bf5b8d4e3ff388ab","tid":2205510,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T01:30:05.000Z","msg":"開個分支繼續討論<br />\n<br />\n原文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2204074\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2204074</a><br />\n<br />\nLet g(n), where n is any positive integer &gt;= 1, be a function such that g(1) = 0.9, g(2) = 0.99, g(3) = 0.999, g(4) = 0.9999 and so on<br />\n<br />\nProve that g(n) = 1 when n -&gt; infinity"},{"pid":"c30b4cc0eb1ab1e522858d6b6844c8a2352f7411","tid":2205510,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T01:59:42.000Z","msg":"g(n) = 9*(10^-1+10^-2+10^-3+...+10^-n) <br />\n<br />\nSum to infinity of geometric series<br />\n<br />\ng(n)= 9 * 0.1/(1-0.1)= 0.9/0.9 =1<br />\n<br />\n係掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bafcce04b40b22201a2f4803e39010196ef085b","tid":2205510,"uid":87557,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T02:22:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g7bugn8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg7bugn8.jpg&h=7c0a7b97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\ngrad咗好多年嘅數學廢j<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3030c08421b713773ac52c41ae01674888d2ba9f","tid":2205510,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T00:38:35.000Z","msg":"push ...."},{"pid":"8916dfc28c7b17de85034da75327e894375dd2f4","tid":2205510,"uid":47901,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bafcce04b40b22201a2f4803e39010196ef085b","tid":2205510,"uid":87557,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"ci